title: rFactor [Jay360UK]
description:
This is rFactor, one of the best racing simulator games for Windows.

To install:

1. Double click setup file and go through installation
2. Run the included update (which must be used in the rFactor directory)
3. Replace the standard .exe with the crack included
4. That&#039;s it! The game should work fine, any problems then leave a comment
